&lt;p&gt;The Petit Palace Opera Garden is notable for its excellent location in the heart of the city next to Las Ramblas, opposite the Gran Teatro del Liceo, in the Gothic Quarter, near the cathedral and Mercado de la Boqueria. A few minutes are in the Olympic Port and the beach.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This modern hotel occupies a completely renovated old building where you can enjoy a sunny garden with trees. Its decoration is nourished by the most innovative design but combined with the details of its ancient structure and modern technological innovations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It has a meeting room with direct access to the garden where you can enjoy the coffees.
The different types of rooms at Hotel Petit Palace Opera Garden Hotel makes it a totally practical, regardless of the client or on a journey that takes place.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before heading out to explore the many attractions of this cosmopolitan city can enjoy the breakfast buffet is served every morning in the breakfast room from 07:30 to 10:30. The buffet consists of:&lt;/p&gt;
